ADMP Adamis Pharmaceuticals Corporation NASDAQ ADMP today announced that the US Food and Drug Administration FDA has acknowledged the receipt of Adamis amendment to its previously submitted New Drug Application NDA for its higher dose naloxone injection product This revision removed EVZIO as a Reference Listed Drug RLD and withdrew the associated Paragraph IV certification Narcan injectable NDA 016636 now remains as the sole RLD and because there are no Orange Book listed patents for NDA 016636 no patent certification is required With this change it is Adamis opinion that the amended NDA will not be subject to a 30month stay and that the FDA will be free to issue an approval as soon as the agency completes a satisfactory review of the Adamis naloxone NDA
